title: S16 Ep79: Supernatural News/Parashare: Lucid Dreams & Alien Themes Edition
itunes:title: Supernatural News/Parashare: Lucid Dreams & Alien Themes Edition
description:
Darkness Radio presents Supernatural News/ParaShare Lucid Dreams & Alien Themes edition

Dave & Tim explore more wacky and wild paranormal stories from around the world, Are Lucid Dreams and Alien encounters connected? The Haunted Tower of London, Goblin Attacks, Willie Nelson's son weighs in on UFOs and Stephen Spielberg admits his fear surrounding the Paranormal Activity movie franchise. PLUS your emails, a BRAND NEW THEATER OF THE MIND and more!

Visit with Dave at these events: www.DarknessEvents.com

Get cool paranormal gear here: www.darknessradio.com/store
